meta.description:
Dr. Sean Brooks breaks down how the mRNA COVID vaccines are going to kill you! 

  At an Ohio school board hearing, a man who identified himself as Dr. Sean Brooks, Ph.D., made several statements concerning COVID-19 immunizations.
 Brooks identifies himself at one point in the video, which you can watch here.

He said, “Dr. Sean Brooks, Ph.D., Oxford. I have 48 publications including 23 books. I’ve studied health medicine, anatomy, and physiology for approximately 21 years.”

He warned parents and board members that those who received the vaccine would die and become sterile.

   Dr. Sean Brooks has a Ph.D. in Education and has a podcast where he discusses American Education.

title: (VIRAL VIDEO) Dr. Sean Brooks Warns Vaccinated Will Die Soon!
